fault_domain_detect_contents:
'#!/bin/sh

  set -o nounset -o errexit

  METADATA="$(curl http://169.254.169.254/latest/dynamic/instance-identity/document
  2>/dev/null)"

  REGION=$(echo $METADATA | grep -Po "\"region\"\s+:\s+\"(.*?)\"" | cut -f2 -d:)

  ZONE=$(echo $METADATA | grep -Po "\"availabilityZone\"\s+:\s+\"(.*?)\"" | cut -f2
  -d:)

  echo "{\"fault_domain\":{\"region\":{\"name\": $REGION},\"zone\":{\"name\": $ZONE}}}"

  '

  '
